<div id="home_loggedout">
  <div class= "jumbotron">
    <div class= "container">
      <%= render "layouts/flash_messages" %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
          <div class= "hero-title">
            <h1>Build a Network Around Your Products</h1>
          </div>
          <div class= "hero-description">
            <h3>Expand your reach by showing how your product works, who uses it now and who else could use it.</h3>
          </div>
          <div class = "hero-button">
            <p><%= link_to "GET STARTED", new_user_registration_path , class: "btn btn-success btn-lg", style: "margin-right:20px"%><%= link_to "LOG IN", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class = "details">
  <div class= "container">
    <div class = "row">
      <div class = "col-md-4">
        <div class="col-padding">
          <i class="fa fa-users fa-2x"></i> 
          <h4>TEAM MEMBERS</h4>
          <p>Add team members that contributed to the product. Coders, Designers, Marketing or Sales - everyone owns a piece of the product and deserves the credit. The more people you add the better you can react to inquiries.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class = "col-md-4">
        <div class="col-padding">
          <i class="fa fa-file-text fa-2x"></i>
          <h4>COLLECT REFERENCES</h4>
          <p>Add a use case with a specific customer. Invite this customer and let them praise your product. There is no better marketing than a happy customer. You can hide their name and only industry, location and size will be displayed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class = "col-md-4">
        <div class="col-padding">
          <i class="fa fa-usd fa-2x"></i>
          <h4>FIND NEW CUSTOMERS</h4>
          <p>Add a desired company that could benefit from your solution. Explain your value proposition for that specific user. Let someone introduce you to the right person there or at similar companies.</p>
        </div>    
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

